node.text: In this video, we compare two brands of moissanite and a natural oval diamond! The two brands are Charles and Colvard and Harro Gem. The diamond is a GIA graded 2ct D VS2 natural diamond. Let us know what you think about the similarities and differences in the comments below!

node.text:
This video compares a 8mm Diamond Cut Harro Gem, 2ct F SI2 “Crushed Ice’l Cushion modified diamond, and an 8mm Cushion Brilliant Forever One Charles and Colvard Moissanite. 
This compares all three stones in direct sunlight, shaded light, and LED Lights.
